  "name": "Combustion",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You ignite a creature in lasting flames. The fire deals 4d8 fire damage and @Damage[2d6[persistent,fire]] damage to the creature, which must attempt a Fortitude save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage and takes no persistent damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage, as well as full persistent damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage, as well as double persistent damage.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> Increase the initial damage by 1d8 and the persistent damage by @Damage[1d6[fire]].</p>"
